_sText:
This is the next generation map of my awp_bunkerfield_beta2 map. There were several
suggestions reguarding my last map that i used in the designing of this map. The
lighting has been improved, unfortuantly i cant get the area bright enough, so the
time set of the battle is a dusk-like time though the bunkers are lit. The awps and scouts 
are now both acessable from the beginning instead of searching for the scouts,
i have also added bunker-busting equipment on a table in the back of the spawn room.
The .nav mesh as be edited so that bots are forced near the weapons closet and therefore
use more than a pistol. Bots do not leave the bunkers, i cannot get them to go up a
ladder and there is no mesh on the ramp leading off of the bunkers.
